alism, or English preferred Minimum 1-2 years' work experience in marketing, communications, or content marketing Editorial mindset that seeks to understand what audiences consume and how to create it. Published content (please provide a portfolio link or work samples) Ghostwriting a published book is preferred. Possess the ability to take existing content and formalize it into magazine/trade publication appropriate pieces. Project management skills and understanding how to manage the priorities of multiple stakeholders in a complex environment and focus on the delivery of results in the form of engagement, leads, and sales. Proficient in MS Outlook, Word, Excel and PowerPoint RECAP: Copywriter Independent Contractor needed for 10-15 hours per week; the expected salary range is $40-$50/hour. Remote work location; however, our company has locations in San Clemente, CA, Corona, CA, and Henderson, NV where we would welcome the right candidate should the location be convenient. ",
